Installing the widget
Download the widget.txt attached

Replace the API key and shopId

Download scriptable on your iPhone

Open scriptable. Create a new script by pressing the plus icon in the top right.

Paste the contents of the widget.txt into your untitled script. (Transfer the file to your phone if you did it on PC)

Press the run button in the bottom right to test if it's working. After that, press "Done" to save it.

Creating the widget
Long press on an empty area in your home screen

Press "Edit" in the top left, then add a widget.

Add a medium scriptables widget (2nd option)

Tap and hold on the widget. Press "Edit Widget"

Under scripts, choose the script you have saved in your scriptable.

andddddddd now you have your komerza widget widget!
